                              <p id="MK.DIR.126">The diocese of Skopje, suffragan to the archdiocese of Vrhbosna (based in Sarajevo, Bosnia and Herzegovina), covers most of North Macedonia. The Bishop is also Eparch for Catholics of the Byzantine Rite in the country.</p>
